	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The first thing to do when asking for contract help from coders is to draft a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Game_design_document" class="postlink">game design document</a>. At an early phase, it might include a brief description of the game play system and story and some mock screenshots. Essentially, it tells us what you want us to help make for you.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
