		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Beechris84 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So it is possible for games to be made on the nes then and people have done so on these forums.</div><br />Yes, this does happen. Most programers aren't &quot;pushing the limits of the system&quot; though... not because of lack of knowledge on how to do so, but lack of time to create something so big. Most programmers figure it's better to keep the scope small and actually finish their games than work on something grandious that will be abandoned along the way.

		

